User & Server

1. User --> Server

    * login / logoff
    * status

2. Server --> User

    * online// offline

3. User --> User

    * direct messages
    * broadcast messages


Commands:

    login <user> <password>
    logoff

    msg <user> body...
    guest: "msg jim hello_world" <-- sent
    jim: "msg guest hello_world" <-- received
